<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>This page outlines how we handle and protect your data in the SMS Processing System.</p>

<h2>Data Collection</h2>
<p>We collect only the necessary information required to process and deliver SMS messages:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Contact phone numbers</li>
    <li>Message content</li>
    <li>Delivery status information</li>
</ul>

<h2>Data Usage</h2>
<p>Your data is used exclusively for:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Processing SMS messages</li>
    <li>Tracking delivery status</li>
    <li>Generating usage reports</li>
</ul>

<h2>Data Protection</h2>
<p>We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your data:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Secure data transmission</li>
    <li>Encrypted storage</li>
    <li>Regular security audits</li>
</ul>